Information security :
- methodologies and policies that
are designed and implimented to protect
data from unauthorized access and damage

Cyber Seucrity:
- methodologies and policies that
are designed and implimented to protect
information systems from unauthorized access and
damage

Nisty Cybersecurity Framework :

s a guidance on how both internal and external stakeholders of organizations can manage and reduce cybersecurity risk. I

NIST Cybersecurity Framework : guidance provided by NIST for the design and implimentatiton of cybersecurity policies and procedures
for managing/reducing cybersecurity related risk.

